<title>FAQs</title>
<div class="page-title">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
</div>

<div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse1">1. What is e-voting ?</a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>E-voting is voting through an electronic system where voters can vote through ballot as per rules and regulations without having the necessity of going and placing the votes manually. Electio has set-up an electronic infrastructure to facilitate voters to cast votes in electronic form through internet.
                    </a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2">2. How will I benefit from e-voting system?</a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p> Paperless mode of casting vote<br>
                    Accuracy in counting votes<br>
                    Substantial reduction in cost, effort and time<br>
                    Elimination of paper ballots

                    </a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse3">3. How will the results be made available at the end of the election?
                </a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>The election commissioner will be able to download the result to keep it as a record which would contain the details like candidate name, votes and total votes.
                    </a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse4">4. How do I register for e-voting facility?
                </a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>The person who is new to the website can register himself as an election commissioner by clicking on register option. Then is needed to enter his name, organization name and he will be registered to the website.

                    </a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse5">5. What is the duration of e-voting period?
                </a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse5" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>The e-voting shall remain open for not less than one day or as specified by election commissioner.

                    </a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse6">6. Can a voter modify a vote already casted before the closing of e-voting cycle?
                </a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse6" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>No. Votes once casted will be considered final and cannot be modified.
                    </a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse7">7.What if I want to conduct a different type of election other than weighted voting?
                </a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse7" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>Elctio provides the facility of choosing the type of election: weighted voting or preferential voting.

                    </a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse8">8. What are the steps to be taken for e-voting?
                </a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse8" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>The Election commissioner of the organization will create an election by placing the schedule like voting start date and end date, withdrawal period, petition duration <br>
                    He will then upload the voters list in the specified file format.<br>
                    System will then send a username and password in the form of e-mail to the voters.<br>
                    Candidates will then file a nomination.<br>
                    Election commissioner will approve the candidate.<br>
                    Election Commissioner will then upload the final candidate list.<br>
                    Voters will then login to the website and has to visit the voting link to cast their vote.<br>
                    After the completion of election voter can view the result. 

                    </a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse9">9.What are the advantages of e-voting to the Organization?
                </a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse9" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>Reduction in cost and paperwork.<br>
                    No need to store physical ballot papers.<br>
                    Accurate counting of votes.<br>
                    Declaration of results in a very short time.


                    </a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse10">10. How the candidates and voters will be notified about the election?  
                </a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse10" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>Election commissioner will announce the election i.e. mail will be sent to the candidate and voter.

                    </a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse11">11. How can the problem be solved if a candidate feels that votes counted are incorrect?

                </a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse11" class="panel-collapse collapse ">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>Candidate feels that the votes counted are incorrect then he can file petition and then whole database will be reviewed by the authorised person. Chance of error is negligible as counting process is computerised.


                    </a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h4 class="panel-title">
                <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse12">12. How the election commissioner can approve the candidate?

                </a>
            </h4>
        </div>
        <div id="collapse12" class="panel-collapse collapse">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>Election commissioner will check the eligibility criteria of the candidate. If a candidate fulfils the criteria then he will be approved else disapproved.
                    </a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>



</div>
